data.description: Completely updated home in great location! Stainless steel appliances to convey. Awesome home with open floor plan, soaring ceilings, tons of natural lights, overlooking beautiful, peaceful creek. LVP in main living areas, gorgeous kitchen with granite countertops, new cabinets, new lighting and fixtures throughout. 2 large bedrooms including additional bonus room/office on main level, main bedroom with ensuite boasting walk in tiled shower. Large rec room downstairs that could be used as additional living space or rented out, complete with bathroom and kitchenette, additional workspace downstairs as well! Covered front porch, sit around the fire pit in the backyard listening to the bubbling creek. With low county taxes and minutes from Sevierville, this is your next home!
